5eea8b8b-e9df-4d69-8ba2-f31402f92b35.title: Satisfactory
5eea8b8b-e9df-4d69-8ba2-f31402f92b35.summary: Satisfactory is a first-person open-world factory building game with a dash of exploration and combat. Play alone or with friends, explore an alien planet, create multi-story factories, and enter conveyor belt heaven!

2c1acc82-c1d1-4dc2-850c-c48feb0bc7ea.title: EVE Online
2c1acc82-c1d1-4dc2-850c-c48feb0bc7ea.summary: EVE Online is a free-to-play community driven space MMO where players can choose their own path from countless different options. Experience space exploration, immense PvP and PvE battles, mining, industry and a thriving player economy in an ever-expanding sandbox.

f3a5770e-c5b0-4ede-a5b1-c7ef615b0aef.title: World of Warcraft
f3a5770e-c5b0-4ede-a5b1-c7ef615b0aef.summary: Miniature Heroes. Colossal Fun. Engage in a dazzling new sensation that's sweeping the inns and taverns across the land with this action-packed mobile strategy
